channel.title: ASF Jira
channel.description: This file is an XML representation of an issue

item.title: [HIVE-22510] Support decimal64 operations for column operands with different scales
item.description: Right now, if the operands on the decimal64 operations are columns with different scales, then we do not use the decimal64 vectorized version and fall back to HiveDecimal vectorized version of the operator. In this Jira, we will check if we can use decimal64 vectorized version, even if the scales are different.
item.summary: Support decimal64 operations for column operands with different scales

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
